OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fdying out this evening. Then dry with
OL,7,Fclear spells and turning rather chilly
OL,8,Fin places. Thickening cloud will bring
OL,9,Frain later in the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FCloudy in the morning with
OL,12,Frain for a time. Dry and somewhat
OL,13,Fbrighter in the afternoon. Further
OL,14,Frain spreading north in the evening.
OL,15,FWarm.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry,
OL,18,Fbright and warm on Friday, chance of
OL,19,Fsome rain on Friday night. Then dry
OL,20,Fand warm over the weekend with some
OL,21,Fbrightness.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
